/*
 * Declarative multi-agent workflow (LangChain4j Agentic) for Quarkus.
 *
 * Requires the quarkus-langchain4j-agentic extension.
 *
 * Example: a support-ticket triage. Two sub-agents analyze a ticket IN PARALLEL
 * (category + priority); a synthesizer combines their findings into a final report;
 * a streaming bridge runs the blocking workflow on a virtual thread and emits progress
 * over a Mutiny Multi; a WebSocket exposes it.
 *
 * This is a multi-file template. Split each section into the file named in its header,
 * under one root package (here org.acme). Replace prompts and types with your domain.
 */

